      "description": "Your personal Stylist— whenever, wherever. Explore app-exclusive content and curated outfit ideas. Unlock exclusive early access to coveted collabs, drops and new product launches. Discover the Closet feature, a living archive of all your Aritzia pieces — and get inspired by our best-dressed community of Aritzia Muses, in-house Stylists and content creators. Plus, the app’s immersive design, intuitive browsing and elevated Product Pages ensure a seamless shopping experience. Clothes are fun — and this app knows it.\n\nKey Features:\nApp-Exclusive Content\nExplore the Style Feed, a shoppable stream of styling inspiration. Discover the latest trends, access expert advice from our very own Stylists, get an insider look at Aritzia’s newest collections and more.\n\nApp-Exclusive Early Access\nBe the first to know — and shop — with early access to our most coveted collaborations, colour drops and new product launches.\n\nCloset\nAnother app-exclusive feature that keeps track of your Aritzia pieces, purchased in-app, in-store and online. See what you have and how to style it, all in one sleek space.\n\nImmersive Design for Endless Discovery\nSo immersive, it’ll feel like you’re at our boutiques. Elevated Product Pages feature Gallery Mode visuals and even audio. Intuitive browsing and endless recommendations help you discover your next favourite style — and 15 after that.\n\nWe use cookies and similar technologies that collect information about your device and track your online activity on our app, our website, and other online services. While the current version of the Aritzia app gives you the right to decide whether or not to permit the use of data used to track you, it does not offer the ability to fully disable cookies.  Even if you do not allow the use of tracking data, Aritzia may use some of your personal information in the app, including to make the app content more relevant to you, which you cannot disable within the app.  By downloading and using this app, you consent to our use of cookies.  Our Privacy Policy explains how you can opt out of certain cookies based on their purpose (including targeted advertising) when you use our website.",
